{"title":"Hello World","date":"2021-02-17T16:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Feb 18, 2021","L":"02/18/2021","MM-DD":"02-18"},"link":"2021/02/18/hello-world","tags":["Hexo","Life"],"categories":["Diary"],"updated":"2021-04-24T14:09:35.621Z","content":"<p>Hello! This is my very first post. I built up my personal blog using <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\" target=\"_blank\">Hexo</a> with <a href=\"https://github.com/ikeq/hexo-theme-inside\" target=\"_blank\">inside</a> theme. I will try hard to make this blog better day by day.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\" target=\"_blank\">documentation</a> for Hexo<br>\n<a href=\"https://blog.oniuo.com/theme-inside\" target=\"_blank\">documentation</a> for Inside</p>\n<h2 id=\"tips-for-using-hexo-and-inside-theme\">Tips for using Hexo and Inside theme<a title=\"#tips-for-using-hexo-and-inside-theme\" href=\"#tips-for-using-hexo-and-inside-theme\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"create-a-new-post\">Create a new post<a title=\"#create-a-new-post\" href=\"#create-a-new-post\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\" target=\"_blank\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"run-server\">Run server<a title=\"#run-server\" href=\"#run-server\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\" target=\"_blank\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"generate-static-files\">Generate static files<a title=\"#generate-static-files\" href=\"#generate-static-files\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\" target=\"_blank\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"deploy-to-remote-sites\">Deploy to remote sites<a title=\"#deploy-to-remote-sites\" href=\"#deploy-to-remote-sites\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html\" target=\"_blank\">Deployment</a></p>\n<hr>\n<p>Updated on April 24th 2021:<br>\nReplacing Weibo Image hosting service with Github + PicGo + JsDelivr.</p>\n","prev":{"title":"Theme Showcase","link":"2021/02/21/Theme-Showcase"},"plink":"http://example.com/2021/02/18/hello-world/","toc":[{"id":"tips-for-using-hexo-and-inside-theme","title":"Tips for using Hexo and Inside theme","index":"1","children":[{"id":"create-a-new-post","title":"Create a new post","index":"1.1"},{"id":"run-server","title":"Run server","index":"1.2"},{"id":"generate-static-files","title":"Generate static files","index":"1.3"},{"id":"deploy-to-remote-sites","title":"Deploy to remote sites","index":"1.4"}]}]}